{"type": "article", "id": 23380, "title": "mad 系列沙发", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-07T07:00:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702153236TsImR4cKPM3jbqDn.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是荷兰设计师 Marcel Wanders 为他的 Mad 系列增加的家具，包括双人沙发、扶手椅等。双人沙发只有半边靠背，是不对称的，从而强调了后面流畅优雅的曲线。而带圆桌面的扶手椅 Mad King 与此同理，因圆桌面打破了对称，让人注意到有曲线的轮廓。另一款 Mad Queen 椅子外形更圆，用菱形网格让椅子表现出装饰感。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153233SYMIdoGTemC16Frn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.62407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153234ZsvoHpwW2AazhYPM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153234fV7klz9syKHhSeRX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153234cZMu2lnk7RNDP30C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153235z4F3XAUYB2tKhNiV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}